OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fsunny spells quickly turning hazy, as
OL,7,Fcloudier skies in Cornwall soon
OL,8,Fdeveloping widely. Showery rain
OL,9,Fsteadily moving east turning heavy and
OL,10,Fpersistent for a time overnight,
OL,11,Fperhaps easing somewhat by dawn.
OL,12,FTurning windy with coastal gales in
OL,13,Fthe west.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FWindy and cool with gales
OL,16,Fpossible, mainly on coasts, perhaps
OL,17,Fbringing some localised disruption.
OL,18,FRain at times though turning much
OL,19,Fdrier through the afternoon, with
OL,20,Fsunnier skies spreading eastwards
OL,21,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
