OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarmer
OL,6,Fon Sunday but breezy and rather cloudy
OL,7,Fwith isolated showers. Hazy sunshine
OL,8,Fpossible at times. Rain arriving
OL,9,Fovernight, perhaps lingering through
OL,10,Fmuch of Monday. Sunshine and showers
OL,11,Fon Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
